        <updateDate>2021-06-15T18:58:33Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Stop the Shutdowns Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Small Business Administration to submit a report analyzing the impact on small businesses of any prospective requirement relating to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) that would restrict or prevent those businesses from operating at normal capacity.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
